[Student "S"]
{NORTH opens 2\C and SOUTH, with 8 points should bid 2\H. 

NORTH should bid his \S suit at his second turn.

And SOUTH can only rebid the 6-card \Hs.

That's enough for NORTH to hear. He bids 6\H, or, just as 
good, he might bid 6NT.}

